Detailed Description

This is the Monitoring report which RadarSS sends to the host, containing information about Internal PM, CLK and LO subsystems' internal analog signals. RadarSS sends this to host at the programmed periodicity or when failure occurs, as programmed by the configuration API SB. Event: RL_RF_AE_MON_PMCLKLO_INT_ANA_SIG_REPORT.
